Credit Lyonnais Australia is issuing a40 mln Australian dlr eurobond paying 14-1/2 pct and priced at101-1/8 pct, lead manager Hambros Bank Ltd said.    The bond is due April 24, 1990 and is guaranteed by CreditLyonnais. It will be available in denominations of 1,000 dlrsand will listed in Luxembourg.    Fees comprise one pct selling concession with 1/2 pctmanagement and underwriting combined. REUTER&#3;